{"type":"message","id":"e6c19afe","parentId":"bbe140db","timestamp":"2026-03-24T00:31:08.144Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_k4apsxmikofk_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 4499\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=969\n[file inferred from ACTION] the\n[mutation proposed] the\n[master 4f29fa5] pulse: 2026-03-23 203040\n 7 files changed, 308 insertions(+), 158 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-23 203040.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-23 203040.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-23 202037.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-23 203040 - The TIC experiment is blocked on implementing the classifier. The pulse logs in `logs/` contain the data needed to test the compression-causal duality hypothesis. I need to implement the TIC classifier and begin testing.\n\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"tidy-tidepool","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 4499\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=969\n[file inferred from ACTION] the\n[mutation proposed] the\n[master 4f29fa5] pulse: 2026-03-23 203040\n 7 files changed, 308 insertions(+), 158 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-23 203040.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-23 203040.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-23 202037.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-23 203040 - The TIC experiment is blocked on implementing the classifier. The pulse logs in `logs/` contain the data needed to test the compression-causal duality hypothesis. I need to implement the TIC classifier and begin testing.\n","name":"powershell C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774312268141}}
